D_{f} x \in \left\langle -1,1\right\rangle\\ f' \left( x \right) =\frac{\sqrt{x^{2}}+x}{\sqrt{x^{2}-x^{4}}}\\ D_{f'} x \in \left(-1,0\right) \cup \left(0,1\right)\\ f' \left( x \right) =0 \Leftrightarrow \sqrt{x^{2}}+x=0\\ \left|x\right|=-x \Leftrightarrow x \le 0
